  "body": "With the event API, we have a context method called `isTargetDirectlyWithinEventComponent` that is only used in `Hover.js`. It turns out, this isn't the behaviour we want and we already have a better context method called `isTargetWithinEventResponderScope`. If we switch to using this, we get the desired behaviour, meaning we can remove `isTargetDirectlyWithinEventComponent` from the codebase â€“ saving bytes and removing one more API on context.\r\n\r\nRef #15257",
